entry.title: U.N. Inspectors Reach Russian-Held Nuclear Plant in Ukraine
entry.content: A team from the International Atomic Energy Agency arrived at the Zaporizhzhia plant despite intensifying fighting along their route, for which Ukraine and Russia blamed each other.

entry.title: Ukrainian Soldiers Say They Are Advancing in the South, but at a Cost
entry.content: Ukrainian army units are pushing toward the city of Kherson, but Ukrainian officials and military analysts have said losses could be high, even if the offensive is successful.
